{"tid":890360,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"（日經）朋友20歲迷途知返 想重新學英文","createTime":"2018-11-05T09:13:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-09T10:52:25.000Z","uid":113546,"like":4,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"a578ccfa68d0ffcb0ca8e1b7b3ce4c859a9886ea","tid":890360,"uid":113546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T09:13:30.000Z","msg":"朋友由幼稚園開始就冇聽過英文堂教啲咩<br />\n到依家20歲了 出嚟做咗幾年嘢<br />\n發現英語水平完全唔得 連基本溝通都好困難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢拼音接近完全唔識噉濟<br />\n26個字母都叫認得<br />\n成日教佢生字 佢過一陣又會唔記得點讀<br />\n但又會記得啲中文意思 睇返個字同提小小又識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n可以點幫佢有有系統噉學返英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n或者有咩書 付費嘅高質字典可以推介一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f1a15427457acfb6d1dd75fc4c9a4b3cd3e1287","tid":890360,"uid":192491,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T09:14:39.000Z","msg":"睇times<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n用有道詞典<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ec416e98a4436d6dcd4540e72d2022ecf9c61cd","tid":890360,"uid":156359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T09:15:26.000Z","msg":"我都係咁"},{"pid":"d0a097048a648065587cd44d5e4985f1ea1645cf","tid":890360,"uid":113064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T09:15:34.000Z","msg":"試下睇D中小學程度嘅英文書先<br />\n最好中英對照"},{"pid":"3f799a1420b7911068b3b3c3fb5e219f4c378a2d","tid":890360,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a578ccfa68d0ffcb0ca8e1b7b3ce4c859a9886ea","tid":890360,"uid":113546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T09:13:30.000Z","msg":"朋友由幼稚園開始就冇聽過英文堂教啲咩<br />\n到依家20歲了 出嚟做咗幾年嘢<br />\n發現英語水平完全唔得 連基本溝通都好困難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\